  ('DK-012', 'FORCE Technology', 'FORCE Technology (GTS)', 'Core Facility', 'DK', 'Brondby', 55.656, 12.409, ARRAY['Advanced Materials','Energy & Climate','Advanced Manufacturing']::text[], ARRAY['Characterization & Metrology','Pilot Line / Scale-up']::text[], 'Fee-for-service', 'Materials analysis, non-destructive testing, metrology, hydro/aerodynamics, Power-to-X / hydrogen test rigs', 'Denmark''s largest registered testing organisation; companies contract materials testing, NDT, metrology and energy/Power-to-X testing across its facilities on a fee-for-service basis.', 'forcetechnology.com', 'approved'),
