  ('LV-004', 'RTU Science and Innovation Centre', 'Riga Technical University (RTU)', 'Core Facility', 'LV', 'Riga', 56.951, 24.093, ARRAY['Advanced Manufacturing','Advanced Materials']::text[], ARRAY['Prototyping / Makerspace','Characterization & Metrology']::text[], 'Fee-for-service', '3D printing, CNC milling, laser cutting/engraving, large-format printing, mould making, materials testing', 'RTU''s Science and Innovation Centre offers a Product Development Unit providing prototyping, mould-making and materials-testing services to industry players and startups, alongside contract research.', 'rtu.lv', 'approved')
